Kim-ku3: Sou2-i2 tioh8 thiann3 ia5-ho5-hoa li2 e5 Siong7-te3, siong5-siong5 siu2 I sou2 hoan-hu3 li2 siu2 e5. (Sin-beng7-ki3 11: 1)
I2-cheng5 u7 chit8-e5 siau3-lian5 ong5. Tu2 chiap i e5 lau7-pe7 cho3 ong5, koat-i3 beh thong2-ti7 i e5 kok cho3 chin-ho2 e5 kok-ka, chiu7 chng-choe3 pian7-sin lang5 chhut ong5-kiong kau3 i e5 kok lai7, si3-koe3 tann2-tham3 kok-lai7 e5 sit8-chai7 su7-cheng5, kau3 kui2-na7 ui7 tham3-thiann chiah-chai, i e5 koann-oan5 chin-choe7 si7 tham-koann u2-li2, pak-siap peh-sinn3, khou2-chhou2 ho2-lang5. U7 chit8-jit8 ti7 soann-kan i2-keng am3, chhoe7 chit8-keng chhu3-a2, chiu7 ka7 phah-mng5. U7 chit8-e5 choh-sit lang5 chhut-lai5, ong5 ka7 i kong2: ¡§Goa2 si7 chhut-goa7-lang5, i2-keng am3 bo5 te3 thang hioh, chhiann2 li2 hou7 goa2 tiam3-chia koe3 chit8-me5 ho2 bo5?¡¨ Hit-e5 lang5 kong2: ¡§Hoan-geng5, hoan-geng5, put-ko3 sou2-chai7 bai2-bai2-a3, ia7 bo5 sim2-mih8 ho2-mih8 thang chiah8.¡¨ Ong5 hit-am3 ti7 hia hou7 in chhiann2 han5-chi5-moe5 phoe3 kiam5-koe-a2, m7-bat chiah8 tioh8 chiah-nih8 bai2, chong2-si7 in-ui7 pak-tou2 iau, ia7 kam2-kak boe7 phainn2-chiah8, chiah8-pa2 ong5 khoann3 chhu3-lai7 e5 cheng5-heng5 kam2-kak tioh8-kiann.
In-ui7 sui-jian5 chhu3, piah phoa3-phoa3, sou2 eng7 e5 mih8-kiann7 chhou-lou2, iau2-ku2 ti7 bin5-chhng5 e5 tu5-a2 nih8 u7 chin-choe7 chheh, koh ti7 tu5-a2 teng2-bin7 u7 chit8-hu3 ku7-ku7 e5 chian3-kah. I chiah mng7 chit-e5 choh-sit lang5, chiah e5 chheh kap chian3-kah si7 siann2 lang5--e5, chit e5 choh-sit lang5 chiah kong2, che si7 i e5, i i2-cheng5 m7-si7 choh-sit lang5, si7 chit8-e5 chiong-kun, i kui2-na7 e5 chiong-kun phoann7 bo5 chiau3 kong-to7, pak-siap, khou2-chhou2 hiah-e5 ho2 peh-sinn3, i ka7 in khoan3-bian2 hoan2-tng2 hou7 in siu7-khi3, ka7 ong5 chau3 i e5 phainn2-oe7, au7-lai5 ong5 thiann in e5 oe7 ka7 i bian2-chit, i koh kong2, ¡§Goa2 bo5 oan3-hin7 ong5, chi2-u7 iu-bun7 sou2 ai3 e5 kok-ka jit8-jit8 teh pai7-hoai7, chong2-si7 thiann kong2 siau3-lian5 ong5 tann che7-ui7, ng3-bang7 i gau5 thong2-ti7 hou7 chit e5 kok-ka khah kong-gi7.¡¨ Siau3-lian5 ong5 thiann-liau2 siu7 toa7 kam2-tong7, keh-jit8 to3-khi3 ong5-kiong, chiu7 sui5-si5 chhut-chiau3 kong2: ¡§Hoan7-na7 iu2-sim ai3-kok e5 chi3-su7, 5 jit8 au7 long2 tioh8 chheng7 chian3-kah lai5 tiau-kinn3 ong5.¡¨
5 jit8 au7, kok-lai7 e5 bun5-bu2 pah-koann long2 chheng7 chin sui2 e5 chian3-kah che5 kau3 ong5 e5 bin7-cheng5. Ki5-tiong chit8-e5, sou2 chheng7 e5 chian3-kah ku7-ku7 senn-sian, tak8-lang5 long2 teh ka7 chhio3, chong2-si7 ong5 chhut-lai5 chiu7 chu3-i3 chit-e5 chheng7 ku7 chian3-kah e5 iong2-su7 beng7-leng7 i chhut-lai5 thau5-cheng5, chiu-ui5 u7 chhio3-siann, chhio3 i chheng7 ku7 chian3-kah, i ia7 tioh8-kiann, liah8-chun2 ong5 beh heng5-hoat8 i le3, thau5 chhih-chhih m7-kann2 giah8-koan5, chong2-si7 ong5 kio3 i giah8-thau5, i chit8-e7 khoann3-tioh8 toa7-kiann, tang-si5-a2 chit e5 siau3-lian5 ong5 si7 cha-jit8 kau3 i e5 chhu3 e5 siau3-lian5 lang5. Ong5 ti7 hit-si5 soan-pou3 kong2: ¡§Chit-e5 lau7 chiong-kun chiah-si7 sit8-chai7 ai3-kok e5 chi3-su7. U7 hak8-bun7 kap iong2-kam2, thiann3 ong5 ia7 thiann3 peh-sinn3.¡¨ Chiu7 beng7-leng7 i kong2: ¡§Chu7 kim i2-au7 phai3 li2 ti7-li2 30 koan7, siong-sin3 li2 tek-khak ti7-li2 chin ho2, ia7 oe7 ho2 khoan2-thai7 it-chhe3 kan-khou2 e5 peh-sinn3.¡¨
Au7-lai5 chit e5 lau7 chiong-kun cho3 30 koan7 e5 te7-hng-koann, ko2-jian5 tiong-kun ai3-bin5, hou7 hit te7-hng e5 peh-sinn3 long2 tit an-ki lok8-giap8, kau3 au7-tai7 lang5-lang5 to teh siau3-liam7 i. Lan2 tioh8 chhin-chhiunn7 chit e5 chiong-kun thiann3 i e5 ong5 an2-ni thiann3 Ia5-ho5-hoa, ia7 tioh8 chhin-chhiunn7 i siu2 ong5 sou2 hoan-hu3 i siu2 e5, lai5 siu2 Siong7-te3 hoan-hu3 lan2 sou2 siu2 e5. (T. T. T. sia2)
